description:
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an enthusiastic, motivated Registered Nurse to join our busy Outpatients team in RGH/YCR. The successful post holder will be able to work across both sites.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post will involve caring for patients within a range of specialities, including, Ophthalmology, ENT, Dermatology, Surgery and Medicine. Applicants must be organised, be able to work as part of a team and have good communication/interpersonal skills. It is desirable, but not essential, to have plaster cast application skills and Outpatient experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ability to speak Welsh is desirable for this post; Welsh and/or English speakers are equally welcome to apply.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing date: 17th November 2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Lynne Edwards&lt;/p&gt;
